title: A Submarine To The Titanic Just Went Missing...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a situation involving a private submarine company offering tours to the Titanic. This company seems to have taken quite an experimental approach to travel that has caused it to go missing and caused a search and rescue operation hoping to find it within a 50 hour window. How did this happen? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
